      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 158,
      "message": "Not sure why the plain java HttpUrlConnection is used, higher level abstractions are used in apex-pdp I think - Apache HttpClient, or jersey's http client could be used here and may be easier to program against it.\n\nIn any case, when using IOStreams, should use the try-with-resources to auto-close them and avoid leaks.",
